CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781287881
OL,3,C'Do not ever use my music': Ariana
OL,4,CGrande tells White House after ICE post
OL,6,FSince then, the White House has
OL,7,Fremoved the audio from the clip and
OL,8,Fappears to have hidden or deleted
OL,9,FGrande's comment.
OL,11,FAddressing Grande's remark, White
OL,12,FHouse spokesperson Abigail Jackson
OL,13,Fsaid in a statement: "We'll say this
OL,14,Fone last time: what's actually
OL,15,Fbarbaric, inhumane, and heinous are
OL,16,Fthe criminal illegal aliens who have
OL,17,Finjured and murdered innocent American
OL,18,Fcitizens."
OL,26,@uD@VOUzD@JO]
