OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781287881
OL,3,C'Do not ever use my music': Ariana
OL,4,CGrande tells White House after ICE post
OL,6,F"Don't ever use my songs to promote
OL,7,Fyour racist, hateful propaganda,"
OL,8,FRodrigo wrote. The song was later
OL,9,Fremoved from the clip.
OL,11,FIn response, the DHS said: "America is
OL,12,Fgrateful all the time for our federal
OL,13,Flaw enforcement officers who keep us
OL,14,Fsafe. We suggest Ms Rodrigo thank them
OL,15,Ffor their service, not belittle their
OL,16,Fsacrifice."
