OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781287881
OL,3,C'Do not ever use my music': Ariana
OL,4,CGrande tells White House after ICE post
OL,6,FRecalling the moment she discovered
OL,7,Fthe clip while scrolling on her phone
OL,8,Fin an interview with Dazed magazine,
OL,9,FRodrigo said: "It was so deeply
OL,10,Fdisturbing to see that propaganda, and
OL,11,Fthe fact it was my song in there made
OL,12,Fme feel even more enraged.
OL,14,F"What they're doing is so awful and
OL,15,Fbarbaric and cruel. I am really sad to
OL,16,Fbe in a country that thinks that's OK."
OL,18,FDuring Trump's campaign in 2016,
OL,19,FBritish pop icon Adele made it
OL,20,Fabundantly clear she did not want the
OL,21,Fnow-president to use her work.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
