OL,3,C'Do not ever use my music': Ariana
OL,4,CGrande tells White House after ICE post
OL,6,FAfter her hit, 'Rolling in the Deep',
OL,7,Fwas played at the Republican
OL,8,Fcontender's rally in Iowa, a
OL,9,Fspokesperson for the singer said:
OL,10,F"Adele has not given permission for
OL,11,Fher music to be used for any political
OL,12,Fcampaigning."
OL,14,FRolling Stones
OL,16,FThe Rolling Stones also told Donald
OL,17,FTrump to stop using their music in his
OL,18,Fcampaign events in 2016, and in 2020
OL,19,Fthe British rock band threatened to
OL,20,Fsue the president for failing to heed
OL,21,Ftheir call.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
