OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781287881
OL,3,C'Do not ever use my music': Ariana
OL,4,CGrande tells White House after ICE post
OL,6,FIn a statement the band said it was
OL,7,Fworking with music rights organisation
OL,8,FBMI to stop the use of their work in
OL,9,FTrump's reelection campaign, and said
OL,10,F"the unauthorised use of their songs
OL,11,Fwill constitute a breach of its
OL,12,Flicensing agreement".
OL,14,FThe band has not appeared to take
OL,15,FTrump to court, and to add insult to
OL,16,Finjury, their hit 'Gimme Shelter' was
OL,17,Fused in 'Melania', the feature-length
OL,18,Fdocumentary about the US president's
OL,19,Fwife.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
