OL,3,C'Do not ever use my music': Ariana
OL,4,CGrande tells White House after ICE post
OL,6,FThrough their record company,
OL,7,FUniversal, ABBA instructed Trump and
OL,8,Fhis team to stop playing their song,
OL,9,F'The Winner Takes It All', at his
OL,10,Fpresidential campaign rallies in 2024.
OL,12,FThey did not give permission, the
OL,13,FSwedish pop legends said, although
OL,14,FTrump's team said they did have
OL,15,Flicenses for the use of music for
OL,16,Fcampaigning purposes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
