OL,3,C'Do not ever use my music': Ariana
OL,4,CGrande tells White House after ICE post
OL,6,FABBA member Bjorn Ulvaeus told ITV
OL,7,FNews Arts Editor Nina Nannar that
OL,8,Fthere is a legal grey area around this
OL,9,Fuse of music, suggesting a legal
OL,10,Fruling is needed to make the rules
OL,11,Fclearer.
OL,13,FLinkin Park
OL,15,FNu-metal pioneers Linkin Park took
OL,16,Flegal action against Trump after the
OL,17,Fpresident retweeted a fan-made video
OL,18,Fusing their song, 'In the End'.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
