OL,3,C'Do not ever use my music': Ariana
OL,4,CGrande tells White House after ICE post
OL,6,F"Linkin Park did not and does not
OL,7,Fendorse Trump, nor authorise his
OL,8,Forganisation to use any of our music.
OL,9,FA cease and desist has been issued,"
OL,10,Fthe band announced in 2020.
OL,12,FPopstar Kesha criticised the White
OL,13,FHouse for using her song 'Blow' in a
OL,14,FTikTok video showing US fighter jets
OL,15,Fattacking ships.
OL,17,FOnce again, the audio has since been
OL,18,Fremoved from the video posted on the
OL,19,Fofficial White House account.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
