OL,3,C'Do not ever use my music': Ariana
OL,4,CGrande tells White House after ICE post
OL,6,FIn a statement posted on X in March,
OL,7,Fthe singer said: "Trying to make light
OL,8,Fof war is disgusting and inhumane. I
OL,9,Fabsolutely DO NOT approve of my music
OL,10,Fbeing used to promote violence of any
OL,11,Fkind.
OL,13,F"This show of blatant disregard for
OL,14,Fhuman life and quite frankly this
OL,15,Fattack on all of our nervous systems
OL,16,Fis the opposite of what I stand for."
OL,18,FCeline Dion
