OL,3,C'Do not ever use my music': Ariana
OL,4,CGrande tells White House after ICE post
OL,6,FIn 2024, Celine Dion's management team
OL,7,Fcriticised the use of the song 'My
OL,8,FHeart Will Go On' at a Trump rally in
OL,9,FMontana.
OL,11,FThe statement, posted on X, said "in
OL,12,Fno way" was the usage of the song
OL,13,Fauthorised and "Celine Dion does not
OL,14,Fendorse this or any similar use".
OL,16,F"... And really, that song?" the post
OL,17,Fadded.
